OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers in
OL,6,Fthe east clearing this evening,
OL,7,Fbecoming dry with clear spells. Cloud
OL,8,Fthickening from the west through the
OL,9,Fearly hours, a chance of some patchy
OL,10,Frain and drizzle in the north towards
OL,11,Fdawn. Winds easing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA rather cloudy start, with
OL,14,Fsome patchy light rain or drizzle.
OL,15,FCloud lifting and breaking through the
OL,16,Fafternoon, with sunny intervals and
OL,17,Fshowers. Noticeably milder with just a
OL,18,Fgentle breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
