OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday, rather cloudy but some
OL,7,Fbrighter intervals. Mostly dry. Mild.
OL,8,FRain moving south overnight, perhaps
OL,9,Flingering but weakening Thursday.
OL,10,FCooler. Friday, variable cloud, patchy
OL,11,Frain easing. Wet and windy later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
